description:
Intertidal coastal habitat types of Namibia (polygons)
Digitised by GreenMap Consultants from colour orthophotos Survey General +  identification of pebble beaches : shape file of Geological Survey of Namibia (based on expert input of Dr O'Toole and Bronwyn Currie). Texture digitised from colour orthophotos Survey General ; wave exposure based on information Rod Braby, weather info and a study of Howes, Harper & Owens (ilmbwww.gov.bc.ca/rics/ pubs/coastal/pysshore)
name: Namibia: Coastal types
